            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>埃森哲(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ACN:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ACN\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ACN-US</a>)截至台北時間03日00:48股價上漲6.57美元，報137.70美元，漲幅5.01%，成交量4,269,306（股），盤中最高價137.70美元、最低價132.94美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.71%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-0.37%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-1.08%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-5.5%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>埃森哲(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ACN:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ACN\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ACN-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+1.53%</li> <li>近 1 月：-33.3%</li> <li>近 3 月：-33.46%</li> <li>近 6 月：-51.13%</li> <li>今年以來：-51.13%</li></ul></section></main>",
